data.description: This stunning home, built in 2022, offers a better-than-new living experience. Fall in love with this 2168sf single-story, open-concept Modern Farmhouse in Verdi with 3 bedrooms and 2 ½ baths. Large, open floorplan with 10’ ceilings and 8’ doors, LVP throughout entire home, top-down bottom-up honeycomb blinds, on-demand hot water, and tons of storage. Gorgeous fireplace upgrade with floor-to-ceiling rock wall. Extra wide foyer/entry hall has upgraded built-in cabinets and shelves. Gourmet kitchen boasts beautiful quartz countertops with full backsplash and modern stainless-steel appliances. With tons of natural light, the kitchen is complete with large island, breakfast bar, and walk-in pantry. Upgrades include additional cabinetry and countertops that extend to the dining area. Main bedroom has separate shower and oversized tub, double sinks, and large walk-in closet. All bedrooms have overhead lights and ceiling fans. Laundry room with sink and cabinets. Enjoy gorgeous sunsets and amazing mountain views from your fully landscaped backyard, complete with large paver patio, lawn area, rock retaining wall, automatic driplines and sprinklers, and gas stub-out for BBQ.  Nestled within a new home development in Verdi, this property is a prime location. It’s conveniently situated with easy access to Highway 80 and offers a seamless commute to both Reno and the California border. Additionally, the beautiful shores of Lake Tahoe are just a short drive away, providing endless opportunities for outdoor recreation and relaxation. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional home your own. Schedule a showing today and discover the perfect blend of style, functionality, and location at 267 Starboard Drive.
